巴西歌手佐佐木艾尔斯在演出中触电身亡https://www.nme.com/news/music/brazilian-singer-ayres-sasaki-dies-after-being-electriccuted-at-show-3776339?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=brazilian-singer-ayres-sasaki-演出时触电身亡Elizabeth AubreyFri, 19 Jul 2024 10:15:08 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3776339 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，这位音乐家在舞台上被浑身湿透的歌迷拥抱后死亡</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brazilian-singer-ayres-sasaki-dies-after-being-electrocuted-at-show-3776339">巴西后歌手艾尔斯·佐佐木 (Ayres Sasaki) 在演出中触电身亡，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>巴西歌手佐佐木艾尔斯在一场演出中触电身亡。</p><p>据报道，35 岁的佐佐木在演出舞台上被一名浑身湿透的歌迷拥抱时触电。</p><p>佐佐木当时正在巴西萨利诺波利斯的一家酒店表演，据报道，风扇的水击中附近的电缆后，佐佐木立即死亡。目前尚不清楚为什么这位歌迷在舞台上拥抱这位音乐家时浑身湿透。</p><p>目前巴西民警正在调查事件具体情况。</p><p>举办音乐会的太阳酒店发表声明称：“我们全力为他的家人提供支持，并采取必要措施。我们重申致力于与主管部门充分合作，以妥善澄清事件。”</p><p>佐佐木的姨妈丽塔·马托斯告诉<a href="https://istoe.com.br/cantor-morre-no-palco-vitima-de-descarga-eletrica-durante-show-no-para/">当地媒体</a>：“我们所知道的是，他的演出原定在特定的时间进行，并且提前了，但我们正在联系当时与他在一起的人，以了解一切是如何发生的。”我们将在一份声明中收集所有信息，并向媒体发布”（来自<a href="https://www.irishmirror.ie/news/world-news/singer-killed-freak-electrocution-stage-33266409"><i>《太阳报</i></a>》）。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CsHdAHtOVRB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554